high_descs: Walk to the left end of the white table.
Pick up the lettuce off of the table.
Place the lettuce on the second shelf in the fridge for a few seconds, take the lettuce back out.
Turn right, walk to the sink.
Place the lettuce to the left of the toaster on the counter.
anns.task_desc: Place the lettuce by the toaster.

high_descs: turn around, walk to the counter, turn right, walk to the side of the table
grab the cabbage on the table
turn right, walk to the refrigerator
open the refrigerator, put the cabbage in, wait a while, take it out
turn right, walk to the toaster
put the cabbage down on the counter by the toaster
anns.task_desc: cool the cabbage in the refrigerator, put it on the counter

high_descs: Turn around and go to the far side of the white table. Turn right, and then right again to face it.
Pick u the lettuce from the right side of the table.
Take the lettuce and turn to the right, then left to find the fridge.
Open the fridge and place the lettuce inside. Shut the door. Open the door and take the lettuce out, then shut the door.
Take the lettuce and turn to the right to find the toaster.
Place the lettuce on the counter to the left of the toaster.
anns.task_desc: Chill a head of lettuce and place it on the counter.
